        </div>
        <div class="exec-stat">
          <div class="exec-stat-label">vs March 2026</div>
          <div class="exec-stat-val" style="color:${mom>=0?'var(--green)':'var(--red)'}">${mom>=0?'+':''}${mom.toFixed(1)}%</div>
          <div class="exec-stat-note">MoM GMV change</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="insight-list">
        <div class="insight-item">
          <div class="insight-dot" style="background:var(--green)"></div>
          <div class="insight-text">Overall GMV of <strong>${fmt(totalGMV)}</strong> achieved <strong>${ach.toFixed(1)}% of target</strong> — the network is above target for April 2026, driven by strong performance from PPP REG5 and ITG stores.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-item">
          <div class="insight-dot" style="background:var(--red)"></div>
          <div class="insight-text">MoM decline of <strong>${Math.abs(mom).toFixed(1)}%</strong> vs March 2026 is significant — March was an exceptionally strong month (+${((62562073000-35327932000)/35327932000*100).toFixed(0)}% vs Feb). April's pullback is partly seasonal post-Ramadan normalization.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-item">
          <div class="insight-dot" style="background:var(--yellow)"></div>
          <div class="insight-text"><strong>${belowTarget.length} stores</strong> are below target this month, with <strong>${belowTarget.filter(s=>s.achP<80).length}</strong> critically below 80%. Priority attention: ${belowTarget.filter(s=>s.achP<80).slice(0,3).map(s=>s.n.replace('Xiaomi Authorized Store ','').replace(' Indonesia','').trim()).join(', ')}.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-item">
          <div class="insight-dot" style="background:var(--blue)"></div>
          <div class="insight-text"><strong>${outperformers.length + onTarget.length} stores</strong> met or exceeded target. Top performers: ${outperformers.slice(0,3).map(s=>s.n.replace('Xiaomi Authorized Store ','').replace(' Indonesia','').trim()).join(', ')}.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="insight-item">
          <div class="insight-dot" style="background:var(--purple)"></div>
          <div class="insight-text">High-end SO of <strong>${totalHE.toLocaleString()} units</strong> and Phone SO of <strong>${totalPhone.toLocaleString()} units</strong> show healthy premium mix. ITG (Mall Taman Anggrek) leads high-end ratio at ${storeAnalysis.find(s=>s.id==='SQID00156')?.mo.h||0} units.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="analysis-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon" style="background:var(--green-bg)">📈</div>
        <div><div class="section-title">What's Up — Stores Beating Target or Showing Strong Growth</div>
        <div class="section-sub">${outperformers.length + onTarget.length} stores on or above target</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="store-analysis-grid">
        ${[...outperformers,...onTarget].map(storeRowHTML).join('')}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="analysis-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon" style="background:var(--yellow-bg)">⚠️</div>
        <div><div class="section-title">What's Down — Stores Missing Target or Declining</div>
        <div class="section-sub">${nearMiss.length + belowTarget.length} stores need attention</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="store-analysis-grid">
        ${[...nearMiss,...belowTarget].map(storeRowHTML).join('')}
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="analysis-section">
      <div class="section-header">
        <div class="section-icon" style="background:var(--blue-bg)">🏢</div>
        <div><div class="section-title">Partner Summary</div>
        <div class="section-sub">Achievement and GMV by distributor partner</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="insight-list">
        ${Object.entries(partnerSummary).sort((a,b)=>b[1].gmv-a[1].gmv).map(([p,v])=>{
          const c = PARTNER_COLORS[p]||'#888';
          const achCol = v.ach>=100?'var(--green)':v.ach>=85?'var(--yellow)':'var(--red)';
          const rec = v.ach>=110?'Excellent — replicate best practices across stores.'
            :v.ach>=100?'On track — maintain discipline and execution standards.'
            :v.ach>=85?'Near miss — review underperforming stores with partner management this week.'
            :'Below target — escalate. Schedule partner review meeting, investigate root causes per store.';
          return `<div class="insight-item">
            <div class="insight-dot" style="background:${c}"></div>
            <div class="insight-text">
              <strong style="color:${c}">${p}</strong> (${v.count} stores) — GMV: <strong>${fmt(v.gmv)}</strong>, Achievement: <span style="color:${achCol};font-weight:600">${v.ach.toFixed(1)}%</span><br>
              <span class="note">💡 ${rec}</span>
            </div>
          </div>`;
        }).join('')}
      </div>
    </div>

